1435
02:03:50,434 --> 02:03:52,894
That's very funny.

1436
02:03:54,146 --> 02:03:55,564
Francesco, you love me?

1437
02:03:57,899 --> 02:04:00,318
I always had a thing for you, Sid.
You know that.

1438
02:04:04,781 --> 02:04:06,867
Your gold shield's
come through.

1439
02:04:35,604 --> 02:04:37,564
What's this for?

1440
02:04:41,151 --> 02:04:43,862
For being an honest cop?

1441
02:04:46,239 --> 02:04:49,409
Or for being stupid enough
to get shot in the face?

1442
02:04:53,830 --> 02:04:56,792
You tell them
they can shove it.

1443
02:05:02,339 --> 02:05:04,216
I don't want it.

1444
02:05:43,130 --> 02:05:44,589
Oh, well.

1445
02:05:49,761 --> 02:05:52,347
Well, Frank,
the facts are these.

1446
02:05:52,431 --> 02:05:56,059
You'll have to stay on leave
of absence for a few months.

1447
02:05:56,101 --> 02:05:59,980
In all probability, the hearing
in your left ear won't come back.

1448
02:06:00,063 --> 02:06:02,691
Two bullet fragments are still
lodged there in the bony portion.

1449
02:06:02,774 --> 02:06:04,401
One is very close to
the carotid artery...

1450
02:06:04,443 --> 02:06:07,237
andyou'll have to be checkked
from time to time.

1451
02:06:07,279 --> 02:06:09,698
Your left side will
feel stiffioccasionally.

1452
02:06:10,866 --> 02:06:14,036
Once in a great while you may
experience some dizziness.

1453
02:06:14,119 --> 02:06:16,246
But in general,
you'll be okkay.

1454
02:06:34,681 --> 02:06:36,975
Through my appearance
here today...

1455
02:06:37,059 --> 02:06:40,062
I hope that police officers in
the future will not experience...

1456
02:06:40,145 --> 02:06:43,732
the same frustration and anxiety
that I was subjected to...

1457
02:06:43,815 --> 02:06:47,110
for the past five years
at the hands of my superiors...

1458
02:06:47,194 --> 02:06:50,113
because of my attempt
to report corruption.

1459
02:06:50,197 --> 02:06:54,951
I was made to feel that I had
burdened them with an unwanted task.

1460
02:06:55,035 --> 02:06:58,580
The problem is that the atmosphere
does not yet exist...

1461
02:06:58,664 --> 02:07:00,624
in which an honest police officer
can act...

1462
02:07:00,666 --> 02:07:05,337
without fear of ridicule
or reprisal from fellow officers.

1463
02:07:05,420 --> 02:07:09,007
Police corruption cannot exist
unless it is at least tolerated...

1464
02:07:09,091 --> 02:07:11,218
at higher levels
in the department.

1465
02:07:11,301 --> 02:07:14,638
Therefore, the most important result
that can come from these hearings...

1466
02:07:14,680 --> 02:07:18,809
is a conviction by police officers
that the department will change.

1467
02:07:19,643 --> 02:07:21,061
In order to ensure this...

1468
02:07:21,144 --> 02:07:24,106
an independent,
permanent investigative body...

1469
02:07:24,189 --> 02:07:27,984
dealing with police corruption,
like this commission, is essential.

